## ════════════════════════════════════════
## BAGIAN C — SKELETON HTML (Jinja2 Template)
## ════════════════════════════════════════

Generate file `templates/themes/{id}.html` dengan struktur berikut.
**Semua data diambil dari variable Flask `inv` (dict invitation) dan `theme` (dict tema).**

### Variable Flask yang tersedia di template:
```python
inv = {
  # Identitas
  "groom_name": str,        # Nama panggil pengantin pria
  "bride_name": str,        # Nama panggil pengantin wanita
  "groom_full": str,        # Nama lengkap pria
  "bride_full": str,        # Nama lengkap wanita
  "groom_parents": str,     # "Bpk X & Ibu Y"
  "bride_parents": str,
  "show_parents": bool,

  # Foto
  "cover_photo": str,       # URL foto cover (dari upload user)
  "groom_photo": str,       # URL foto portrait pria
  "bride_photo": str,       # URL foto portrait wanita

  # Akad
  "akad_date": str,         # "2025-08-17"
  "akad_time": str,         # "08:00"
  "akad_venue": str,
  "akad_address": str,

  # Resepsi
  "resepsi_date": str,
  "resepsi_time": str,
  "resepsi_venue": str,
  "resepsi_address": str,

  # Lokasi
  "maps_url": str,          # Google Maps link
  "maps_embed": str,        # Google Maps embed URL

  # Konten
  "love_story": str,        # JSON string [{title, date, content}]
  "music_url": str,         # YouTube / direct audio URL
  "slug": str,              # URL identifier undangan

  # Computed (via template filter)
  "photos": list,           # [{filename, is_url, caption}]
  "gifts": list,            # [{bank_name, account_number, ...} or {ewallet_type, ...}]
}

theme = {
  "id": str,
  "name": str,
  "palette": dict,          # {"Nama": "#hex"}
  "fonts": dict,
  "assets": dict,
}

# Jinja2 filters tersedia:
# {{ inv.akad_date | format_date }}  → "Sabtu, 17 Agustus 2025"
# {{ inv.akad_time | format_time }}  → "08.00 WIB"
# {{ inv.cover_photo | photo_url }}  → URL lengkap foto
# {{ guest_name }}                   → nama tamu dari query param ?to=NamaTamu
```

### Struktur section WAJIB ada:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <!-- Meta, fonts Google, CSS tema -->
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ① ENVELOPE / COVER — Layar pembuka sebelum undangan "dibuka" -->
  <section id="cover-screen">
    <!-- Tombol "Buka Undangan" dengan animasi reveal -->
    <!-- Nama tamu: {{ guest_name or "Tamu Undangan" }} -->
  </section>

  <!-- ② HERO — Nama pasangan + foto cover + countdown timer -->
  <section id="hero">
    <!-- {{ inv.groom_name }} & {{ inv.bride_name }} -->
    <!-- Countdown ke resepsi_date -->
  </section>

  <!-- ③ PASANGAN — Foto + biodata singkat groom & bride -->
  <section id="couple">
    <!-- groom_photo, bride_photo, groom_full, bride_full, parents -->
  </section>

  <!-- ④ ACARA — Detail waktu & lokasi akad + resepsi -->
  <section id="event">
    <!-- Akad: akad_date, akad_time, akad_venue, akad_address -->
    <!-- Resepsi: resepsi_date, resepsi_time, resepsi_venue, resepsi_address -->
    <!-- Tombol "Lihat Peta" → maps_url -->
  </section>

  <!-- ⑤ LOVE STORY — Timeline momen pasangan (opsional, tampil jika ada data) -->
  {% if inv.love_story %}
  <section id="lovestory">
    <!-- Parse JSON love_story, render timeline -->
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- ⑥ GALERI — Foto-foto dari invitation_photos -->
  {% if inv.photos %}
  <section id="gallery">
    {% for photo in inv.photos %}
      <!-- render tiap foto -->
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- ⑦ RSVP — Form konfirmasi kehadiran -->
  <section id="rsvp">
    <!-- POST ke /rsvp/{{ inv.slug }} -->
    <!-- Fields: guest_name, attendance (hadir/tidak), guest_count, message -->
  </section>

  <!-- ⑧ HADIAH DIGITAL — Bank transfer & e-wallet (opsional) -->
  {% if inv.gifts %}
  <section id="gifts">
    {% for gift in inv.gifts %}
      <!-- render tiap rekening/ewallet -->
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- ⑨ FOOTER — Ucapan penutup, credit -->
  <section id="footer">
    <!-- "Dibuat dengan ❤️ oleh habarkita.com" -->
  </section>

  <!-- FLOATING: Music player (jika music_url ada) -->
  {% if inv.music_url %}
  <div id="music-player">
    <!-- Tombol play/pause audio -->
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- JS: GSAP, parallax, partikel, countdown, lightbox, RSVP fetch -->
</body>
</html>
```

